LAST-MODIFIED:20260204T193014Z
UID:217993-1771585200-1771592400@www.seattleparksfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Camp Long - Ivy removal
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Camp Long. \nCamp Long needs a little tender love attention\, especially after the fire which destroyed the lodge. We will finish removing ivy from the plantings along the parking lot at the entrance. Then we will move to an planting area behind the lodge as well as single spots around the lodge. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/camp-long-ivy-removal-2/
LOCATION:WA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/home-NEW-2-Catherine-Anstett-Trolls-Knoll-gloves.jpg
