SUMMARY:Friends of Discovery Park
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Discovery Park. \nCapehart Forest is the most wildlife-diverse area in Discovery Park. Come help us promote forest health and increase its biodiversity by weeding out invasives\, mulching and aerate the soil to encourage symbiotic fungi\, and plant this year’s native shrubs and groundcovers. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/friends-of-discovery-park-3/
LOCATION:WA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/friends-of-discovery-park_356-d9sgne.jpg
END:VEVENT
